  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0ddd \u0d9c\u0dab\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dc4\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Liter counting down",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro Gas Company says that the price of a Litro domestic gas cylinder will be reduced by 100 to 200 rupees from midnight tomorrow (5).",
        "Mr. Muditha Peiris, the president of the company, said that this price reduction will be done according to the gas price formula introduced by Litro Gas Company, the Ministry of Finance and the Consumer Affairs Authority.",
        "The chairman said that this price reduction will be done according to the current gas prices in the world market and also mentioned that the price of gas cylinders of all sizes will be reduced.",
        "The chairman who said that Litro Gas Company has made a significant profit in the past two months, also said that the company has made a huge profit of 70 crore rupees in the last month of August alone."
      ],
